But there is more to that legend, time is relative and Young Link's frame data doesn't care about your timing. There is rumors that after completing his destiny in teaching his descendant in Twilight Princess, that Young Link was given the choice to save yet another realm from certain doom. In the World of Light, he could redeem himself.

Equipped with his trusty tunic and Phrygian cap, he has everything he needs to take down the Master Hand and then some.